title: The God Who Wasn't There - The Myth of Jesus Christ
description:
Documentary filmmaker Brian Flemming examines the Bible and discusses the history of early Christianity, raising doubts as to whether the New Testament personage Jesus ever really existed. 

Flemming examines the similarity of the Jesus story to other saviour myths of the time and points to inexplicable gaps in early Christian history that combine to shed doubt on the Bible's Jesus story. 

Written by Martin Lewison.



Enjoy and Seed!!
